    <h3>New Legend: OCTANE</h3>
    <p><em>High-Speed Daredevil</em></p>

    <blockquote>
       <p>If it doesn’t involve diving, leaping, plummeting, or racing, then Octane wants nothing to do with it. Always the life of the party, Octane truly believes winning the Championship isn’t enough… not if you didn’t cheat death at least twice to get there.</p>
