    <h3>Razer Chroma Support</h3>
    <p>Apex Legends will now detect Razer Chroma peripherals and supported devices will now play animated colors that react to things you do in the game! Some examples:</p>
    <ul>
       <li>Red lights during banner transitions.</li>
       <li>While skydiving colors will tune to the color of your smoke trail.</li>
       <li>Picking up loot.</li>
       <li>Opening Apex Packs</li>
       <li>Firing and taking damage.</li>
       <li>Colors that flash when your Ultimate is ready.</li>
       <li><em>And more!</em></li>
    </ul>
